---
slug: specifying-the-cluster
id: fjuasdxyavzw
type: challenge
title: Starting Your Appliance Configuration
teaser: Enable and configure the embedded cluster
notes:
- type: text
  contents: Let's build a Kubernetes appliance
tabs:
- id: fuunbnxuyib8
